node.text: Attention coffee lovers! There's a NEW video on the tube with 3 refreshing iced coffee recipes 🤤. We also share some flavoured milk recipes that'd be delicious with hot coffees and teas as well! How do you prefer your coffee in the summer? Hot or cold? ☀️ Check out the video with the link in profile 🤗 #coffee #icedcoffee #vegan #plantbased

node.text:
There's a NEW video on the tube! 🥰⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Moving away from Canada is not something I ever thought I'd do. I moved to the Netherlands for love, but it came with a considerable amount of heartache in missing my family, along with an ongoing nagging feeling that I would need to eventually learn Dutch. I'll say frankly that language learning is not an interest of mine, but in order to be able to continue to stay in the Netherlands, I was required to learn a basic level of Dutch. I was given a generous few years by the government to learn the language, but silly me kept postponing studying. I think in my heart I kept thinking Robin and I would move back to Canada before the deadline approached. But that didn't happen. And the cherry on top: the deadline even got pushed up 5 months, so I had only about 1 week to cram in learning as much Dutch as I possibly could 🇳🇱⁣
⁣
This is that story. Plus the video features the incredible @nathanieldrew_ 🕺🏻 Video link in profile! 🎥 ⁣⁣

node.text: Got some overripe bananas on your counter? This recipe is a delicious way to use them up 🍌🤤! If you couldn't be bothered to make  an entire loaf, or if it's super hot where you are and you'd rather not heat up the house by turning on the oven, then give this speedy, single-serving dessert a try. Recipe link in profile 😊 Happy Friday! #vegan #plantbased

node.text:
Heyooo there’s a NEW videooo💃🏻 whoop whoop!⁣
⁣
We’ve made 3 new meal prep breakfast recipes that are so good, I don’t think I can pick a favourite. There’s a savoury recipe, a cool and refreshing recipe, and a crunchy chocolatey recipe 🤤⁣
⁣
And as if that weren’t enough, we also posted an extra 3 recipes to the website too! A homemade salsa, some baked tortilla chips, aaaand an unbelievably delicious chipotle refried bean recipe 🔥 6 new recipes in one day? Oooh ya 😌⁣
⁣
Check out the video with the link in profile 🙌 #vegan #plantbased #breakfast

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sadia Badiei, BSc Dietetics on May 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, food and indoor.

node.text:
There’s a NEW video on the tube 😁 3 EPIC salad recipes, with the most easy and delicious 7-ingredient homemade vegan feta you’ll ever try🤤 plus I share my personal formula for making an incredible salad that impresses every time 😉⁣
⁣
We made this video thinking it’d be perfectly in time for the heat of late spring, but it’s been so cold and grey in the Netherlands that I’m still wearing my winter jacket out and about, and I have a blanket on my lap at my desk as I type this 😅. Looking forward to a bit of sun, not gonna lie. How’s the weather been where you’re at? ⁣
⁣
Check out the video with the link in profile 🥒🫐 #vegan #plantbased

node.text: What's better than a homemade soft, chewy cookie? 🍪 A skillet-sized, crunchy-on-the-outside, soft-and-chewy-on-the-inside cookie, filled with gooey caramel! 😏 Dig into this epic dessert this weekend 🙌 Full recipe breakdown is linked in profile. What's your favourite kind of cookie? #vegan #plantbased #dessert #cookies #baking

node.text: The first time we tested this recipe, Robin took a bite, his eyes widened and he asked, “Wait, is this dessert or breakfast?”. That pretty much sums up this recipe 😏. It’s creamy, filling, wholesome, and tastes like having dessert for breakfast 🍓! The full recipe breakdown is linked in profile 🙌 Have you tried any of our overnight oats recipes yet? #vegan #plantbased #breakfast

node.text: In the mood for a fluffy, warm, bakery-style blueberry muffin 🤤? This recipe comes together with under 10 ingredients and in under 10 minutes! Add everything to your favourite mug, mix, microwave it, and you’re ready to gobble it up 🫐l! Full recipe breakdown with the link in profile 💙🙌 #vegan #plantbased

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sadia Badiei, BSc Dietetics in Pick Up Limes. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
Oh hey there 🙋🏻‍♀️ There's a NEW plant video up on the tube 🪴😆⁣
⁣
When I was younger, my mum had LOADS of plants all around our home, but I never cared to learn about plant care from my mum back then (facepalm, I know 🤦🏻‍♀️).⁣
⁣
So when I finally got some plants of my own, I made a bunch of mistakes and killed a whole lot of them 😅. I still make mistakes of course, but it’s getting easier and easier to keep them thriving 🌱.⁣
⁣
In the video I share tips I wish I had learned sooner in keeping plants alive and happy 🤓 Check out the link in profile! 🌿 #plants #houseplants #plantcare

node.text: My new favourite nut butter: cashew butter 🤩 it’s so smooth and velvety and caramel-like. It’s our new secret weapon in making overnight oats and smoothie bowls go from tasting great to tasting absolutely incredible 🤤 only one ingredient needed, and ready in under 20 minutes 🙌 recipe link in profile! #vegan #plantbased
